{"tid":1251761,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣] 你話暴政？邊撚到暴啊？","createTime":"2019-06-22T16:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T01:54:43.000Z","uid":97155,"like":120,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"e5e21be2d8182c5e6764dc2ded76aea1f7e57ee7","tid":1251761,"uid":97155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"[文宣] 你話暴政？邊撚到暴啊？<br />\n長文多字<br />\n 希望各位花心機睇理性討論下 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為我地既抗爭籌集資本 另外要counter一下呢個政權既招數</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢一兩日港府再同大家玩拖延戰之餘又大興輿論戰扮弱者搞Reputation management 主要既目的大家都知 就係為左<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">消磨抗爭者既民意</span></span> 同埋 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏 無立場 或者 立場唔堅定既人既支</span></span>持<br />\n<br />\n上面既嘢我相信唔洗我講大家都知 而獨媒 文宣組 同埋抗爭者都好努力咁將個事實放緊係眼前 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">點解喺呢一場同政權角力既輿論戰仲係好似佔緊下風？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左「裝睡的人叫不醒」呢個原因之外<br />\n我地都應該去推敲一下呢啲工作未達成效既原因 <br />\n之後再去諗下點去應對 以支持我地唔同方式既抗爭！<br />\n<br />\n以我既觀察加上同朋友討論之後覺得原因有<br />\n<br />\n<strong>其一 呢啲所謂中間派對某啲媒體有偏見</strong><br />\n正如我地唾棄大公文匯 東方太陽一樣 佢哋仍然有人覺得蘋果同獨媒等等係有外國勢力或者既定立場 所以好自然咁選擇唔相信佢哋嘅報導<br />\n<br />\n<strong>其二 我哋部份嘅文宣工作太內向</strong><br />\n我哋之前嘅文宣工作 成品大部份<span style=\"color: red;\">不停只係喺同路人之間廣傳然後再沉底</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇錯 的確喚醒同路人都好重要 的確係可以令到抗爭更加可持續 但係<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果要對抗政權嘅輿論戰的話 一啲向對立意見或者冇意見嘅人嘅宣傳就更加重要</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>其三 中間派中左政權同官媒嘅計</strong><br />\n政權係輿論戰一邊重咗一啲枝節<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">淡化左成件事嘅重心</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">例如 : 佢哋會將焦點放左係衝擊嘅行為上邊 而忽略咗衝擊背後嘅原因係政府漠視訴求同埋制度失衡 ; 或者係放咗喺抗爭者暫時阻礙社會運作 而睇唔到成個議題長久對民主自由社會嘅影響</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>其四 好多人對事件既了解一知半解</strong><br />\n好多人都只係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">睇標題或者係聽電視新聞講幾句就算</span></span> 從來冇去查證過事實 所以先至會有覺得政府 <span style=\"color: red;\">「道咗歉 暫緩咗 回應咗」</span>嘅謬誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>其五 部份人對社會價值唔了解</strong><br />\n好多中間派 尤其係上咗年紀嘅人 <span style=\"color: gold;\">對於民主社會珍而重之嘅社會價值 (法治 自由同公民權利 投票 三權分立 等等) 認識唔深</span> 所以難以了解今次事件甚至係成個制度嘅不公義 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更加理解唔到制度上嘅暴力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>其六 有啲同路人都未醒</strong><br />\n有啲同路人對於成個議題又或者係成個制度嘅崩壞依然係一知半解 唔了解成件事嘅嚴重性同埋逼切性 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">令到抗爭唔持續同失焦</span></span> 而係中間派詢問嘅時候又難以比到一個有條理嘅答案說服佢哋支持<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得而家除左我地之前做開既抗爭同聚焦係反修例同fact check既文宣之外<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真係有需要花啲心機向所有人做下教育</span></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然多字內容好多 <br />\n但係我相信同路人會有心機睇 <br />\n亦都相信中間派甚至對家都總有人可以有能力分析現實<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可能好理想 希望只要我地目標只要一致 路線唔怕多 大家盡力應該可以做到啲改變</span></span>"},{"pid":"0884b28dea1eabedccd0447a1cc91069eda293e9","tid":1251761,"uid":97155,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:35:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實我自己之前都喺 ig同fb鳩噏左少少嘢 <br />\n叫做整合左少少同<span style=\"color: red;\">呢個政權有幾扭曲 制度有幾崩壞同唔可靠 最終迫使我哋走上呢條抗爭嘅路</span>有關既事</span><br />\n<br />\n想各位同路人可以花少少時間睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完之後 希望可以真係講得出<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢一個暴政 究竟暴喺邊一度</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">再話比身邊既同路人或者其他人講下<br />\n喚醒下教育下佢地 喺佢地唔相信我地既媒體既時候<br />\n我地既關係 可能已經係我地最大既武器</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw我枝筆同整圖唔叻 各位有手足有乜提點希望可以幫手！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95efe6b015dd6bd720dad9b36545acd205463807","tid":1251761,"uid":265467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:36:34.000Z","msg":"[請廣傳]香港只有真普選先可以趕走港共政府同建制派賣港賊!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251736</a>"},{"pid":"db3bcf6dd582740693a4ffb44ec67fa1daab9137","tid":1251761,"uid":97155,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真係好多圖好多字！！請大家耐心睇下！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xUbtcHz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxUbtcHz.png&h=0d28d505&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WeUFOfV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWeUFOfV.png&h=309d1424&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/myvqeVW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmyvqeVW.png&h=b3db91e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ERLtW9h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FERLtW9h.png&h=25292cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hs8bUVZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhs8bUVZ.png&h=1097c86e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tTr1xHF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtTr1xHF.png&h=5c60f9d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MG7oL2G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMG7oL2G.png&h=1a1ad564&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HqPizV2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqPizV2.png&h=0d887b1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/23/003919_fd28ab00b116e6e83dc22b96466ac77e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F23%2F003919_fd28ab00b116e6e83dc22b96466ac77e.png&h=c3d7f615&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/23/003921_cabf5df4f7a74f66e16aff9340e26dc0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F23%2F003921_cabf5df4f7a74f66e16aff9340e26dc0.png&h=e88f34a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b094779484e5855adef9b5dea1d5170b2b09c5c","tid":1251761,"uid":97155,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AFtjjn1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAFtjjn1.png&h=67c90d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tmyrJPH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtmyrJPH.png&h=8c2065a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBszSH4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvBszSH4.png&h=9ee8f875&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CkUyoPL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCkUyoPL.png&h=f1fa8352&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ODC8cH6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FODC8cH6.png&h=8b568f33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T9EeSH7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.